attributes.action: Pause plans for Oxford-Cambridge rail link pending a full, independent review
attributes.background: We do not want the Oxford-Cambridge rail link as described in the East West Rail Company's Route Update Announcement and subsequent refinements. We call for these plans to be paused and for a full, transparent and independent review.
